title: Episode 7: Allie, Chelsey, and Molly (three more of our PSI Talks speakers)
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this episode of 'Psychology and Stuff', Dr. Ryan Martin talks with the other three speakers for the upcoming PSI Talks (blog.uwgb.edu/uwgbpsych/psi-talks/). Allie Nelson, Chelsey Steffens, and Molly Swenty share why the decided to submit a talk, how they are feeling about the event, and (with no spoilers) what they plan on talking about.
